- backend/app/main.py
- backend/app/routes/*.py
Action:
- Keep phase order unchanged.
- Replace non-deterministic text with IF/THEN actions.
- Preserve non-contradiction constraint: no auth redesign, no media-control-plane route modification, no non-audit route source override.
Expected output:
- Deterministic rule list for execution.
PASS condition:
- No rule contains open-ended verbs (for example, "reconcile", "improve", "fix", "handle") and no step requires human interpretation.
STOP if:
- Any rule requires manual choice not already encoded in this file.

EXPECTED PHASE BOUNDARY CONDITIONS
- DO NOT modify media_control_plane routes or docs.
- DO NOT remove routes referenced in control-plane docs.
- Auth routes may only be aligned to security baseline.
- Do NOT stop at catalog-only status unless the file path is in media-control-plane docs.
- Do NOT add new phases or reorder step IDs.
